OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FIt handles around 40,000 criminal
OL,7,Fcases every month in England and
OL,8,FWales, according to the Magistrate
OL,9,FAssociation, and they cannot result in
OL,10,Fa prison sentence.
OL,12,FPreviously, defendants were expected
OL,13,Fto go to court for these minor
OL,14,Foffences, but the system was changed
OL,15,Fin 2015 in order to reduce pressure on
OL,16,Fthe courts and minimise the stress and
OL,17,Ftime commitment for defendants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
