OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FHowever, it has since been labelled a
OL,7,Ffast-track justice system and there
OL,8,Fare increasing concerns over its lack
OL,9,Fof transparency, the speed at which
OL,10,Fsome magistrates review cases, and the
OL,11,Fprosecution of vulnerable people.
OL,13,FA joint investigation by ITV News and
OL,14,Fthe Evening Standard revealed how
OL,15,Fflaws in the system were resulting in
OL,16,Fpeople being wrongly prosecuted behind
OL,17,Fclosed doors.
