OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FThere are growing calls for the system
OL,7,Fto be urgently reformed - including
OL,8,Ffrom the former Lord Chief Justice who
OL,9,Foversaw its introduction.
OL,11,FHow does the Single Justice Procedure
OL,12,Fwork?
OL,14,FThe Single Justice Procedure was
OL,15,Fintroduced by the Criminal Justice and
OL,16,FCourts Act 2015.
OL,18,FIt deals with cases involving adult
OL,19,Fdefendants accused of the least
OL,20,Fserious type of crimes - known as
OL,21,Fsummary-only offences.
