OL,6,FHowever, Ministry of Justice data
OL,7,Fshows that it is rare that cases are
OL,8,Fsent back to prosecutors, as reported
OL,9,Fby the Evening Standard.
OL,11,FMagistrates cannot dismiss a case
OL,12,Fwhere there is a guilty plea,
OL,13,Faccording to the Ministry of Justice.
