OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAn investigation by ITV News and the
OL,12,FEvening Standard uncovered a
OL,13,Fsignificant number of "micro
OL,14,Fmiscarriages of justice", mainly in
OL,15,FDVLA and TV Licensing offences, where
OL,16,Fpeople are being convicted despite
OL,17,Fhaving strong mitigating circumstances.
OL,19,FWe selected 50 cases where defendants
OL,20,Fwith strong extenuating circumstances
OL,21,Fhad still been convicted under SJP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
