OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,F"It is clear from the cases that I
OL,7,Fhave reviewed that some people have
OL,8,Fticked the guilty box through a lack
OL,9,Fof understanding of their rights and
OL,10,Fhow their mitigating circumstances may
OL,11,Fbe relevant to guilt. A chronic lack
OL,12,Fof investment in the criminal courts
OL,13,Fmust never be allowed to serve as an
OL,14,Fexcuse for unjust outcomes in our
OL,15,Fcriminal justice system."
