OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FZayd Ahmed, barrister at Mountford
OL,7,FChambers, said: "Having considered the
OL,8,Fcases provided to me by ITV, the SJP
OL,9,Fis undermining the fundamental
OL,10,Fprinciples of justice and due process
OL,11,Fby shortcutting what all these
OL,12,Fdefendants expected to be protected
OL,13,Ffrom, the right to a fair trial.
OL,15,F"It is my opinion that most of the
OL,16,Fcases I have considered should not
OL,17,Fhave even gone to Court, let alone
OL,18,Fresulted in a conviction."
