OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FWhat are the concerns about the system?
OL,8,FThere are concerns over the lack of
OL,9,Ftransparency of SJP, as when
OL,10,Fdefendants plead guilty the cases are
OL,11,Fheard in private - and therefore
OL,12,Fjournalists and members of the public
OL,13,Fare not allowed to attend.
OL,15,FProsecutors often do not see the
OL,16,Fmitigating circumstances - as they are
OL,17,Fcurrently not required to read these -
OL,18,Fand therefore often do not withdraw
OL,19,Fcases that are not in the public
OL,20,Finterest to prosecute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
