OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FMany members of the Magistrates'
OL,7,FAssociation have said they are
OL,8,F"uncomfortable" with the system and
OL,9,Fthat a "significant proportion" say
OL,10,Fthey do not always have enough time to
OL,11,Fproperly review cases.
OL,13,FITV News and the Evening Standard also
OL,14,Ffound mistakes in the system that led
OL,15,Fto the conviction of at least one
OL,16,Fperson this year who was already dead.
