OL,3,CThe Single Justice Procedure: What is
OL,4,Cit and why are there calls for reform?
OL,6,FReforms proposed by the Magistrates
OL,7,FAssociation include the requirement
OL,8,Fthat prosecutors look at pleas and
OL,9,Fmitigations before cases are reviewed
OL,10,Fby the magistrate, improving training
OL,11,Ffor magistrates and allowing SJP
OL,12,Fsittings to be observed by journalists.
OL,14,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,15,Fthe Ministry of Justice said: "The
OL,16,FSingle Justice Procedure was designed
OL,17,Fto allow low-level offences to be
OL,18,Fdealt with simply and without people
OL,19,Fhaving to go to court unless they
OL,20,Fchoose to do so.
